00:02:03.951 --> 00:02:05.642
- Pazitorul zanelor.

10
00:02:05.677 --> 00:02:07.265
Pastratorul secretelor.

11
00:02:09.301 --> 00:02:10.647
- Colonelul Schneider.

12
